### Get all benefit plans
GET http://localhost:8081/benefits/plans

### Get plan by ID
GET http://localhost:8081/benefits/plans/1

### Get plans by type - Medical
GET http://localhost:8081/benefits/plans/type/Medical

### Get plans by type - Dental
GET http://localhost:8081/benefits/plans/type/Dental

### Get plans by type - Vision
GET http://localhost:8081/benefits/plans/type/Vision

### Get enrollments for employee 5001
GET http://localhost:8081/benefits/enrollments/employee/5001

### Get enrollments for employee 5000 (should have no Medical - MOD 7 == 0)
GET http://localhost:8081/benefits/enrollments/employee/5000

### Get enrollments for plan 1 (Titanium Health PPO)
GET http://localhost:8081/benefits/enrollments/plan/1

### Get enrollments by plan type - Medical
GET http://localhost:8081/benefits/enrollments/type/Medical

### Count enrollments for plan 1
GET http://localhost:8081/benefits/enrollments/plan/1/count

### Count enrollments by plan type - Medical
GET http://localhost:8081/benefits/enrollments/type/Medical/count

### Count enrollments by plan type - Dental
GET http://localhost:8081/benefits/enrollments/type/Dental/count

### Count enrollments by plan type - Vision
GET http://localhost:8081/benefits/enrollments/type/Vision/count

### Enroll employee in a plan
POST http://localhost:8081/benefits/enrollments
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "employeeId": 5000,
    "planId": 3
}

### Unenroll employee from a plan
DELETE http://localhost:8081/benefits/enrollments/employee/5000/plan/3
